# 🏦 Banking Regulatory Reporting Data Platform (GCP)

---

**📐 Architecture**

| Component | Description |
|----------|------------|
| GCS | Raw data storage layer |
| BigQuery | Bronze, Silver, Gold layers |
| Cloud Composer | Airflow orchestration |
| Terraform | Infrastructure as Code |

---

**📊 Dataset**

| Source | Description |
|-------|------------|
| Czech Financial Dataset (Kaggle) | Banking data (accounts, transactions, loans) |

---

**✨ Key Features**

- Medallion Architecture  
- External Table → Raw Table ingestion  
- Partitioned BigQuery tables  
- Data Quality Checks  
- Regulatory reporting layer  

---

**🔄 Pipeline Flow**

| Step | Description |
|------|------------|
| 1 | Data ingestion → GCS |
| 2 | External table validation |
| 3 | Bronze load |
| 4 | Silver transformation |
| 5 | Gold reporting |

---

**🛠️ Tech Stack**

| Category | Tools |
|---------|------|
| Cloud | GCP (BigQuery, GCS, Composer) |
| Infra | Terraform |
| Processing | SQL |
| Orchestration | Airflow |
| Language | Python |

---

**🚀 How to Run**

| Step | Action |
|------|-------|
| 1 | Terraform apply |
| 2 | Upload data to GCS |
| 3 | Trigger Airflow DAG |
